  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I picked myself 16 girls who was working outside work, because here at least I knew that is inside work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Train to Germany.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when they been in the room--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because there was a doctor had here-- there his laboratorium, or whatever, ever he did the experiments in this camp, in another camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the-- one woman who was working there, like a nurse, her name was Mila Portashinski, she was intelligent girl.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, Magda, they-- how can they make-- find out that?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They must kill us first and open the brain, and then find out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it's not a sanatorium, what he promised.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It will be all finished at crematorium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew that it won't be so easy, but I thought, I-- they know that they are going to death, and I just opened the door.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So their death or my death-- I let them out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I take the risk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they arrived to the train, two was missing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that started the story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that happens.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They, they wanted to kill me or to hang me or to shoot me, because this is sabotage.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How dare I let the girls out?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And next to the Barrack 10 was Barrack 11, and this was where they hang or shoot or killed or whatever the [INAUDIBLE] or any enemies to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there as a hangman was a Jewish wrestler by the name [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jakov. ?] And he sent me a message that he will do it quick.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was thinking how, but going backwards, the Greek girls who was there with the experiments, they been so grateful because I helped where I could before the operation or after operation.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
